    "title": "Data Scientist / Data Engineer",
    "description": "<h2>Company Description</h2>\n<p>Here at YouGov we have the best data and the best tools. We continuously challenge conventional approaches to market research, and we disrupt our industry to ensure that our clients always get the best solutions.</p>\n<p>Specific to this role you will be working in a cutting edge data science and R&amp;D heavy skunkworks project within YouGov. If you like data, ML, AI and, working with brilliant colleagues, you will really enjoy yourself in this role.</p>\n<h2>Job Description</h2>\n<p>We're looking for a software / data engineer with a data analyst mindset to join our lovely team at YouGov Signal!</p>\n<p>Scope of work:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Research, analyse and assess data</li>\n<li>Design algorithms and aggregates</li>\n<li>Work with the product owner, figure out how to turn raw data into required deliverables</li>\n<li>Generate and research data product ideas</li>\n<li>Build proof of concept solutions to validate the ideas</li>\n<li>Work closely with the development team on production implementations</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Qualifications</h2>\n<p>Experience:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>At least 2 years in the field or in a similar field (If you have more experience we will pay accordingly as we are hiring for multiple roles)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Skills/requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Software / data engineering skills</li>\n<li>Well organised &amp; methodical</li>\n<li>Good communication in English: both written and verbally</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Nice to know:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Python</li>\n<li>Experience with AWS Big Data tools and services</li>\n<li>Spark and Hive</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Additional Information</h2>\n<p>Location: WFH, preferably Poland, but anywhere in Europe is fine (the candidate will be working with mostly Polish people, but they are all fluent in English).</p>\n<p>Salary is very competitive.</p>\n<h2>Interested?</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://vonq.io/37Usowo\">Click here for the application form!</a></p>\n",
