    "description": "<p><strong>Company background</strong></p>\n<p>We craft our own Blockchain solutions for established companies that want to solve major challenges of their industries.</p>\n<p>This is an opportunity to be one of the first to join a startup created by three outstanding founders that have worked both for startups (raising more than $100m from top tier investors worldwide), for venture capital funds (managing over €100m in assets under management) and for large enterprises (leading technologic developments in a variety of fields).</p>\n<p>We focus on delivering solutions highly relevant to actual business needs of our partners and that can be of use for entire industries.</p>\n<p>We believe in having small teams of outstanding professionals, always with a focus on personal growth of each of them, and sharing the company's success with our team.</p>\n<p>As a software engineer at Clariteia:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You will work directly with one of the cofounders and CTO, who previously lead Blockchain development for one of the largest European companies.</li>\n<li>You will work in a core project for one major player in the music industry.</li>\n<li>You will be able to work on a variety of functionalities and technologies:</li>\n<li>Blockchain: distributed databases based on graphs, consensus algorithms and digital certificates.</li>\n<li>Data science: fraud detection systems, search engines and predictive recommendations.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Role Specifics</strong></p>\n<p><em>Minimum qualifications:</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Experience as a technical influencer for highly scalable distributed system designs.</li>\n<li>Experience with coding in data structures, algorithms and software design.</li>\n<li>Experience using cloud platforms and/or containerized application deployments.</li>\n<li>Experience delivering complex, large scale and critical products with business impact.</li>\n<li>Experience in Microservices Architecture.</li>\n<li>Experience in working agile methodologies.</li>\n<li>Write well designed, testable, efficient code.</li>\n<li>Professional experience of cloud platform hosting via AWS / GCP as well via terraform / cloudformation / helm.</li>\n<li>Experience with Python</li>\n<li>gRCP</li>\n<li>AsyncIO</li>\n<li>CLI development</li>\n<li>Flask/Falcon</li>\n<li>Familiar with Kafka</li>\n<li>Familiar with common CI/CD like Jenkins, Bamboo, Spinnaker.</li>\n<li>Familiar with common monitoring / alerting / logging tools such as Prometheus, Datadog, ELK stack, distributed tracing.</li>\n<li>Fraud Dection Algorithms</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>A Plus qualifications:</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li>C</li>\n<li>Rust</li>\n<li>Blockchain</li>\n<li>AI</li>\n</ul>\n",
    "how_to_apply": "<p>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:andrea@clariteia.com\">andrea@clariteia.com</a></p>\n",
