    "description": "<p>Trade Republic is a European platform for mobile investing. With its intuitive app, people can save, invest, and trade on the capital markets commission-free with just three taps. Trade Republic's vision is for everyone to have the opportunity to take managing their investments into their own hands.</p>\n<p>Trade Republic is a bank licensed in Germany and supervised by the Bundesbank and BaFin. Their cooperation with well-known partners such as HSBC, BlackRock, and solarisBank underlines the high quality and security of their service. Trade Republic's investors include Accel, Creandum, Founders Fund, and Project A, as well as sino AG.</p>\n<p><strong>What you'll be doing</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Working with our existing Android team to help build new and maintain existing features in the Trade Republic app</li>\n<li>Being involved in our feature processes, working closely with the product and design team to help refine our new features</li>\n<li>Work in a fast paced agile environment, where you will have the opportunity to take on responsibilities and ownership</li>\n<li>Work closely with other team members, helping to mentor, develop and grow the team</li>\n<li>Bringing your existing knowledge and best practices to enrich the knowledge and experience in the team</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>About You</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>You have at least 5 years experience in software engineering</li>\n<li>You have experience with RxJava, along with a strong understanding of the Kotlin and the Android Framework</li>\n<li>You care about quality, and know the best ways to achieve this both in code and for the product itself</li>\n<li>You have an eye for detail and a passion for a great UX and UI, you are keen to work closely with our designers and product team to achieve this</li>\n<li>You have a team focused approach, wanting to share knowledge and help develop others in the team further</li>\n<li>You enjoy working in an agile environment and have a self-driven personality with a “hands-on” approach</li>\n<li>You are a well rounded software developer who understands the importance of communication</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Tech Stack</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>100% Kotlin</li>\n<li>RxJava3</li>\n<li>MVVM</li>\n<li>Dependency Injection (Dagger2) and wide unit test coverage</li>\n<li>Retrofit/OkHttp</li>\n<li>WebSockets with a custom protocol, that bridges the reactive contract over the network</li>\n</ul>\n",
    "how_to_apply": "<p><a href=\"https://traderepublic.join.com/jobs/1632934-senior-android-engineer-m-f-d?pid=357a3b4531918760973f&amp;utm_source=github_jobs&amp;utm_medium=paid&amp;utm_campaign=single%2Bposting&amp;utm_content=senior%2Bandroid%2Bengineer%2Bm%2Bf%2Bd\">https://traderepublic.join.com/jobs/1632934-senior-android-engineer-m-f-d?pid=357a3b4531918760973f&amp;utm_source=github_jobs&amp;utm_medium=paid&amp;utm_campaign=single%2Bposting&amp;utm_content=senior%2Bandroid%2Bengineer%2Bm%2Bf%2Bd</a></p>\n",
