    "description": "<h2>RESPONSIBILITIES</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Researching, designing, implementing and maintain our new product’s backend (in Java\necosystem).</li>\n<li>Understanding and documenting the existing product (in Ruby on Rails).</li>\n<li>Find ways for a reliable infrastructure/product, implement and ensure them.</li>\n<li>See yourself as a user and recommend improvements for the existing product.</li>\n<li>Be part of developing the whole company culture and mindset.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>YOUR PROFILE</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Software development is not a science for you where many years of university are required for – you see it as a craftsmanship which you have to practice over and over again.</li>\n<li>You see a product not as parts – you see it as one thing and want to take ownership for it.</li>\n<li>Meaningful and solid experience with the Java environment (Ruby on Rails is a plus).</li>\n<li>Fluent in English (German is a plus).</li>\n<li>Knowledge about German taxes and/or law is a plus.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>OUR OFFER</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Tech stack:\n<ul>\n<li>Java ecosystem</li>\n<li>Kubernetes on AWS</li>\n<li>GitLab (repository, CI/CD, images, packages, issue tracking),</li>\n<li>Postgresql</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Be part of an international, professional and growing team.</li>\n<li>Be able to really contribute to the architectural and product decision process.</li>\n<li>And everything else you expect from a Tech Startup located in Berlin Kreuzberg: regular team events, office kicker as well as free drinks and fruits. :-)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>ABOUT US</h2>\n<p>wundertax simplifies the filing of taxes for everyone. With our state-of-the-art online tool, we help our customers to do their taxes fast, simple and without the need for an expensive tax advisor. As a result, we already generated more than 200 million euros in tax refunds for our customers.\nNext to our general employee tool, wundertax operates several target specific online portals such as for students, police officers, soldiers or trainees to respond to the different needs of our users. We also operate the leading English-language portal for expats.</p>\n",
