    "title": "(Senior) Frontend Developer (f/m/d)",
    "description": "<p>as of now | full time | unlimited contract</p>\n<p>YOUR MISSION AS A FRONTEND DEVELOPER (F/M/D) AT LILLYDOO</p>\n<p>Together with your 18 colleagues your mission is to evolve our LILLYDOO website to the next level! Therefore, you are in constant contact with our Marketing, Project Management and Digital Product Department. As a part of the Development Team you take care of expanding our e-commerce platform so that we are always able to offer our customers the perfect purchasing experience. Furthermore, we offer you an open environment to evolve and implement your ideas. Rise to these exciting challenges with us, here at LILLYDOO!</p>\n<p>WHAT YOU SHOULD BRING</p>\n<ul>\n<li>At least four years professional experience in the area of UX design and frontend development</li>\n<li>You share our commitment to quality, work according to test based development and are disciplined in maintaining documentation</li>\n<li>You are fully competent in both written and spoken in English</li>\n</ul>\n<p>WHAT MAKES YOU STAND OUT</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Experience with an e-commerce platform</li>\n<li>Ideally you have also knowledge of Bootstrap, PHP &amp; Symfony</li>\n</ul>\n<p>WHAT WE OFFER YOU</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Work-Life-Balance:\n30 Days of Holiday, Mobile Working, flexible working hours</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Office Life:\nTeam Events, Collective Monday Breakfast, Fruit Baskets, Big Variety of Drinks, HelloFreshGo Vending Machine</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Personal Benefits:\nFree Diaper Subscription for parents, Optional Givve Credit Card or Fitness First Membership (after probational period), Corporate Benefits Account, Babble Account, Company Pension (20% Employer Contribution), Relocation assistance and Visa Support</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>THAT DISTINGUISHES US</p>\n<p>„Within the dev team you can find a second family, everyone is eager to help out and support one another wherever they can. We value quality over quantity, share our knowledge with each other and let the best ideas win”\nAlex from the Development Team</p>\n",
    "how_to_apply": "<p>YOUR CONTACT AT LILLYDOO</p>\n<p>Pia | Senior Talent Acquisition Expert | <a href=\"mailto:career@lillydoo.com\">career@lillydoo.com</a></p>\n",
